<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/966148-at-the-end-of-the-book-it-is-implied-that">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[At the end of the book, it is implied that Morrie was the one who stole the money from Bernard's secretary. While I can understand the resentment that Morrie had for his brother, unless I missed something, I don't quite understand what he would have against his secretary.<br /><br />Anyone have any thoughts? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
